1. *Shvatate* li šta pokušavam da vam kažem? (Do you *understand* what I'm trying to tell you?)
2. Ne mogu da *shvatim* zašto mi se ovo dešava. (I can't *comprehend* why this is happening to me.)
3. Molim vas da *shvatite* ozbiljno ovu situaciju. (Please *take seriously* this situation.)
4. Da bi *shvatio* njegove namere, moraš da ga bolje upoznaš. (In order to *understand* his intentions, you have to get to know him better.)
5. Svi moraju *da shvate* koliku opasnost predstavlja ova bolest. (Everyone needs *to realize* how dangerous this disease is.)
6. Upravo sam *shvatila* da sam izgubila svoj telefon. (I just *realized* that I lost my phone.)
7. *Shvatićete* da ne možemo učiniti ništa više u ovom trenutku. (You will *see* that we cannot do anything more at this moment.)
8. Neću *shvatiti* ako me ne podržite u ovome. (I won't *understand* if you don't support me in this.)
9. Molim te da *ne shvataš* sve tako lično. (Please *don't take* everything so personally.)
10. Ako *shvatim* tvoje pitanje pravilno, odgovor je ne. (If I *interpret* your question correctly, the answer is no.)